      "message": "good question, but what should happen instead is common.BucketPermissions should accept project and (short) bucket name.\n\nWhen common.BucketPermissions was originally written, we used long bucket names which were supposed to included a project name, e.g. luci.infra.try for what will now be called (project\u003dinfra, bucket\u003dtry).",
