      "writtenOn": "2019-12-18T23:16:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "From https://osscs.corp.google.com/chromium/infra/infra/+/master:go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/milo/buildsource/builder.go;l\u003d35?q\u003dbuildsource%2Fbuilder.go\nThe 2nd token, which contains no \u0027/\u0027, is passed to common.BucketPermissions.\nIt seems like the long bucket name is still being used?\nIn that case, we can\u0027t really just change the signature of common.BucketPermissions now, am I right?",
      "parentUuid": "294ac673_61fcb6a1",
      "range": {
